snippet.title: Best VGM 731 - Nostalgia - Hanging Gardens of Babylon
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 624 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t97-JQtcpRA
Best VGM 1618 - http://youtu.be/VmemS-mqlOQ

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo DS
Nostalgia (2009)
Hanging Gardens of Babylon
Shinichiro Sato & Rei Kondoh
